{"tid":478932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"降關稅減少來港掃貨？中國客：香港買東西還是安心一點","createTime":"2017-11-24T14:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T23:31:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a95195c146ae3917b5a96b9c2a3f7ddc1cdd97eb","tid":478932,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"內地下月起實施新政策，大減進口消費品關稅，部份訪港內地客熱購產品例如奶粉配方更毋須再付關稅，而化妝品亦減低了進口關稅。長居紐約的北京遊客邱先生指，相信內地旅客來港購買化妝品是因為品質好，非因為價錢平。「有很多來港買化妝品的人，不完全因為價格，或許因為香港的標準比內地好一點。好像我來香港買東西，並非因為價格，而是因為品質，心裏比較安心一點」。他指今次公幹只是順道替朋友購買化妝品。<br />\n<br />\n來自遼寧的鄭小姐替內地朋友買化妝品，認為內地旅客會繼續在港買化妝品，「還會買，（因為）安全問題吧，因為香港品質和選擇比較多，不是價格問題」。<br />\n<br />\n來自深圳的林小姐指，現時內地的化妝品無論價錢或品質與價錢，已經和香港相若，不會因內地減稅而影響消費模式。不過，她指來港的內地旅客都只是順道購物，而非刻意，「內地不少化妝品也很好，不一定要來香港買，但來香港的話，就順便逛逛」，她又指現時有不少網上代購商，本身網上購物的人不會來港購買化妝品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171124/57501189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F57501189&d=1jv8LJm6VaFhRmhi9skO%2BjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e355a1e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F57501189&h=b82f1f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171124/57501189</a>"},{"pid":"35c46009860ea7f8124eda954e457f12c91c5d77","tid":478932,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死返上去"},{"pid":"2c528896d2e54a414799f3a8d14cbc7b0237fcf6","tid":478932,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"又話中國強大了，死返去支持你地嘅國貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d006f44ef19538918fde94c9464f882c3e1a5479","tid":478932,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"又話愛國"},{"pid":"235d0deeff9ba2b40010e5d15fc1e1564812eb6e","tid":478932,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"操你媽大陸狗"},{"pid":"04321a7276cffd7d35c99dbafd4da0427be3e92a","tid":478932,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T23:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}